data.description: ***SELLERS TO CONTRIBUTE 4K TOWARDS BUYERS CLOSING COSTS/ RATE BUY DOWN IF CLOSING BY MID FEBRUARY*** Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 2-bath Craftsman cottage home bursting with character and vibrant, beautiful colors. This cozy abode offers a warm and inviting atmosphere that's sure to make you feel right at home. Here's a glimpse of what this delightful property has to offer.  (INSIDE) The spacious and sunlit living room has large windows, offering plenty of natural light. Gleaming floors throughout, complemented by vibrant and tasteful wall colors. This open concept design seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen. Kitchen possess ample counter space for food preparation and casual dining. Four generously sized bedrooms are each adorned with its own unique scheme and character. Primary bedroom features an en-suite bath for added convenience and privacy with large, pass-through walk-in-closet to convenient laundry room.  (OUTSIDE) A private and completely fenced-in backyard oasis is perfect for entertaining, gardening, or simply relaxing on the largest lot in the neighborhood. The back patio has room for outdoor grilling overlooking the expansive backyard! This friendly and vibrant neighborhood is ideal for walks and socializing. Come see your new home today!
